# ClarityDSM does NOT read the API key from an env var or bundle it into the
# build. The key is entered in-app (the key button, top-right) and stored only
# in the browser's localStorage on the user's own device. There is nothing to
# put here for normal use — this file is a placeholder.
#
# If you later move to a shared key behind a server-side proxy (so colleagues
# don't each need their own key), set the proxy origin here and point
# src/lib/anthropic.js at it:
# VITE_PROXY_URL=https://your-proxy.example.com
